[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0185","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0185.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0073","title":"SGI IRIX Telnet 环境变量注入安全绕过漏洞","description":"IRIX 系统 telnet 服务存在安全绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 telnet 协议向目标系统发送包含 LD_LIBRARY_PATH 等环境变量的特制请求，绕过系统正常库加载机制，最终获取 root 权限并完全控制目标主机。该漏洞影响 IRIX 操作系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0073"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-10-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.050","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 安全公告对应的 telnetd 补丁，或升级至不受影响的 IRIX 版本。如无法立即打补丁，在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行并重启 inetd 以禁用 telnet 服务；同时移除 telnet 的 setuid root 权限作为临时缓解。建议全面迁移至 SSH 替代 telnet 进行远程管理，并在边界防火墙上封锁 telnet 端口（23/TCP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0073","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/02/24/3","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/03/07/3","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2026/03/08/6"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0185.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0184","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0184.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0668","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 ActiveX TypeLib 控件远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 的 scriptlet.typelib ActiveX 控件被错误标记为\"对脚本安全\"（Safe for Scripting），远程攻击者可构造恶意网页诱导用户访问，利用该控件绕过安全限制执行任意命令。该漏洞已被 Bubbleboy 蠕虫在野外利用，通过电子邮件传播，影响所有安装 Internet Explorer 5 的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0668"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.493","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-032 对应更新，为 scriptlet.typelib 控件设置 Kill Bit（CLSID: {AE24FDAE-FF06-11D0-8646-0000C0008E86}），阻止其在 Internet Explorer 中加载。对于已停止支持的 IE 版本，建议升级至受支持版本或禁用 ActiveX 脚本功能。如无法更新，可在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 下为上述 CLSID 添加 Compatibility Flags 值为 0x400 的 Kill Bit 项作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ240308","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/598","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-032","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19468"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0184.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0184.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0184.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0183","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0183.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0610","title":"Webcart CGI 程序信息泄露漏洞","description":"Webcart CGI 程序存在配置不当漏洞，攻击者可利用不安全的访问控制直接获取 Webcart 购物车系统中的敏感信息，包括用户订单详情、联系信息等。该漏洞影响使用 Webcart CGI 的早期电子商务网站，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程访问，属于信息泄露类安全缺陷。建议修改 CGI 脚本权限配置并实施访问控制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0610"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.933","remediation":"立即检查服务器上是否仍在运行 Webcart CGI 程序，若无需使用则彻底删除或禁用该 CGI 脚本。如业务必须保留，应限制 CGI 目录权限为仅可执行必要文件，配置 Web 服务器（如 Apache）通过 .htaccess 或 location 指令限制可访问 IP 范围，并禁用目录列表与符号链接跟随。同时建议迁移至现代受支持的电商平台，避免使用已停止维护的 CGI 程序暴露敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0610","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0610.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/webcart.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0610.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--99fbdaa8-4c6c-4442-9bb2-6a51e40a9543.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0183.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0183.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0182","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0609","title":"SoftCart SoftCart.exe CGI 配置不当信息泄露漏洞","description":"SoftCart 电子商务软件的 CGI 程序 SoftCart.exe 存在错误配置漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 请求利用该配置缺陷，获取服务器上的敏感信息（如订单数据、客户信息等）。该漏洞影响使用 SoftCart CGI 程序的 Web 服务器，CVE 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。建议升级软件版本或限制 CGI 脚本访问权限进行修复。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0609"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.817","remediation":"将 SoftCart 订单数据存储目录移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /var/softcart/data），通过 Apache 的 <Directory> 指令或 .htaccess 的 Deny from all 禁止直接访问该目录；将文件权限设置为 600，仅允许 Web 进程用户读取。由于 SoftCart 已停止维护，建议迁移至支持敏感数据加密存储的受支持购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0609","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0609.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0609.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2055/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c26f55c1-1cb8-453a-ae44-fe71d70ff34b.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/InfoSecWarrior/Vulnerable-Box-Resources/blob/c784bcf63e1ec5c3a0116043d8653d00f0a21a0b/Vulnhub/OZ/oz-1-nikto-8080-output.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0182.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0181","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0072","title":"IBM AIX xdat 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 xdat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 xdat 程序发送特制的超长输入参数，触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用，成功利用后可完全控制受影响的系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0072"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.907","remediation":"立即安装 IBM 为该漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（对应 AIX 4.x 及更早版本的 xdat 缓冲区溢出修复），或升级到包含该修复的 AIX 维护级别。临时缓解措施：执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/xdat` 移除 xdat 的 setuid root 权限，阻止非授权用户以 root 权限执行该程序；如业务不需要 DMI（Desktop Management Interface）子系统，可卸载相应文件集或禁用 xdat 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0072"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0181.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0180","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0608","title":"PDG Shopping Cart 信息泄露漏洞","description":"PDG Shopping Cart 的 CGI 程序 shopper.cgi 存在配置不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用错误的访问控制配置直接访问未授权的敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用了 PDG Shopping Cart 的早期 Web 服务器，攻击者无需身份认证即可窃取用户订单数据、购物车内容等隐私信息。厂商未提供官方修复补丁，建议升级至更安全的购物车系统或移除不必要的 CGI 脚本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0608"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.690","remediation":"立即移除或替换已停止维护的 PDG Shopping Cart，升级至现代受支持的购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）。若无法立即替换，在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）配置中对 shopper.cgi 添加 IP 白名单访问控制，并移除 CGI 目录的目录浏览权限，防止未授权访问泄露敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","http://www.pdgsoft.com/Security/security.html.","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3857","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0608","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0608.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jwx2-gr93-39wv/GHSA-jwx2-gr93-39wv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0608.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0180.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0180.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0178","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0178.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0607","title":"QuikStore quikstore.cgi 敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"QuikStore 购物车系统的 quikstore.cgi 脚本将敏感配置文件 quikstore.cfg 存储在 Web 文档根目录下且未设置充分的访问控制措施，导致远程攻击者可直接通过 HTTP 访问该文件，获取管理员明文密码并进而获得系统管理权限。该漏洞影响 QuikStore 购物车应用，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0607"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.570","remediation":"立即将 quikstore.cfg 移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /etc/quikstore/），并通过 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache 的 <FilesMatch> 或 .htaccess）禁止公开访问 .cfg 文件；设置文件权限为 600，仅允许 Web 服务器运行用户读取；由于 QuikStore 已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至仍受支持的现代购物车系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0607","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0607.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/q/quickstore.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0607.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1983/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ba5d6d065e4a7a2829bd0ee4eca4f1c8ca12a28d/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0178.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0178.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0178.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0176","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0605","title":"Order Form 1.0 购物车 CGI 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Order Form 1.0 在线购物车 CGI 程序存在配置不当漏洞，远程攻击者可通过直接访问该 CGI 脚本的特定配置文件或未授权的 URL 路径，获取购物车系统中存储的客户订单信息、交易记录等私密数据。该漏洞属于信息泄露类型，攻击条件简单，无需认证即可利用，影响使用该购物车程序的 Web 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0605"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.337","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器上移除或禁用 `order_form.cgi` 脚本。修改 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）配置文件，限制对 CGI 目录的访问权限，添加 IP 白名单或 HTTP 认证。如仍需购物车功能，应升级至支持安全配置的现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce 等），并确保 CGI 脚本不以全局可读权限运行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0605","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0605.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw/GHSA-vhcv-cv27-25rw.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2021/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0176.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0176.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0175","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0175.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0070","title":"Apache NCSA HTTPd test-cgi 目录遍历信息泄露漏洞","description":"Apache 0.8.x/1.0.x 及 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 中的 test-cgi 程序存在目录列表泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发该脚本的目录遍历功能，获取服务器上任意目录的文件列表，进而导致敏感信息（如配置文件、脚本源码等）泄露。该漏洞影响早期版本的 Apache 和 NCSA HTTPd 服务器，利用方式简单，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0070"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.563","remediation":"升级到 Apache 2.0 及以上版本（该问题在 Apache 1.3.x 已修复），或直接移除 test-cgi 脚本及所在目录的执行权限。同时禁用 Apache 中 Options 指令的 Indexes 参数，防止目录列表泄露。如无法升级，在 httpd.conf 中将 test-cgi 目录的访问控制设置为 Deny from all。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/rc5d27fc1e76dc5650e1a3f1db1de403120f4c2d041cb7352850455c2%40%3Cusers.httpd.apache.org%3E","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20435","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0070.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0070.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0070","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0070.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/c8b30957414aefbd6ba0b766db0d40593ba36fba/references/CVE-1999-0070-2023-09-21-1730","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0070.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0070.md","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-93fg-xppj-x2xf/GHSA-93fg-xppj-x2xf.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0070.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0175.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0175.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0174","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0174.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0604","title":"Selena Sol WebStore 1.0 信息泄露漏洞","description":"WebStore 1.0 购物车 CGI 程序 web_store.cgi 存在配置不当漏洞，由于该 CGI 脚本未正确限制文件访问权限，远程攻击者可通过直接构造特制 HTTP 请求访问服务器上的敏感文件，导致私密信息（如配置文件、数据库凭证等）被非授权泄露。该漏洞影响 Selena Sol WebStore 1.0 版本，攻击无需认证，利用难度低，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0604"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:43.217","remediation":"立即停用 WebStore 1.0，迁移至支持数据库后端存储（而非文件存储）的现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）；如无法立即替换，须将 web_store.cgi 生成的订单数据文件移出 Web 文档根目录（如移至 /var/lib/webstore/），设置目录权限为 700、文件权限为 600，并通过 Web 服务器配置拒绝外部直接访问数据文件路径，同时在搜索引擎中请求移除已索引的敏感信息缓存。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92462991805485&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0604","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0604.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0604.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88033/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000611.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0174.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0173","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0173.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0595","title":"Microsoft Windows NT/2000 页面文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows NT 及 Windows 2000 操作系统在关机时未清除系统页面文件（pagefile.sys）中的残留数据，导致内存中的敏感信息（如明文密码、密钥、用户数据等）可能被写入磁盘并长期保留。本地攻击者在获取系统访问权限后可通过读取页面文件提取这些敏感信息，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0595"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-01-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:42.143","remediation":"通过本地安全策略启用「关机：清除虚拟内存页面文件」（路径：安全设置→本地策略→安全选项），或设置注册表 HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Session Manager\\Memory Management\\ClearPageFileAtShutdown 为 1。建议升级至 Windows 2000 SP4 或更高版本以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/216","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0595","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0595.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0595.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c/GHSA-79qg-vhxm-8q4c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86259/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0173.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0172","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0172.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0585","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 默认管理员账户漏洞","description":"Windows NT/2000 系统的内置管理员账户默认名称为 \"Administrator\"，该账户名在系统中为公开已知且无法通过常规方式修改。攻击者可利用这一已知账户名，结合弱口令爆破或字典攻击，远程尝试登录目标系统。由于攻击者无需猜测用户名，仅需破解密码即可获得管理员权限，这显著降低了暴力破解的难度。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 和 Windows 2000 系统，虽然 CVSS 评分较低，但在实际攻击中常被用作信息收集和初始入侵的突破口。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0585"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2000-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.933","remediation":"重命名默认 Administrator 账号为其他名称，并创建一个名为 Administrator 但无实际权限的诱饵账户；同时启用账户锁定策略，在 30 分钟内 5 次登录失败后锁定 30 分钟，以防范暴力破解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0585","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0585","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0585.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w6jm-mv22-w3jr/GHSA-w6jm-mv22-w3jr.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0585.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152600_152700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4f1e8558-005f-464b-a513-8b0f99604c5f.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0172.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0171","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0493","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.statd RPC 调用转发漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 的 rpc.statd 服务存在远程 RPC 调用中继漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送恶意的 SM_MON 和 SM_NOTIFY 命令将 RPC 调用转发至本地操作系统，进而利用该中继机制触发 automountd 等其他组件中的安全缺陷。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0493"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.887","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00186 提供的修补程序（Solaris 2.5.1 SPARC: Patch 103691-01, x86: Patch 103692-01）。如无法立即打补丁，可编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释掉 rpc.statd 行后重启 inetd 以禁用该服务，或在防火墙层面限制对 RPC portmapper（端口 111/tcp 和 111/udp）的入站访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91547759121289&w=2","http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/186&type=0&nav=sec.sba","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-99-05-statd-automountd.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-045.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/450","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19327"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0170","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0069","title":"Sun Solaris ufsdump/ufsrestore 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 ufsdump/ufsrestore 工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，拥有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过向该工具传递特制参数触发溢出，覆盖内存数据，进而实现权限提升或以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，CVSS 评分 8.4，危害等级高危，需系统本地账号方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0069"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.363","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至 Solaris 8 及以上版本，或安装 Sun 官方补丁 106880-01 (SPARC) / 106881-01 (x86)。临时缓解措施：限制 ufsdump/ufsrestore 的 setuid 权限，仅授权管理用户执行文件系统备份操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/169","http://www.osvdb.org/8158","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19534","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0069","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0069.md","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-0069_0f0c3530-7572-4860-a943-991d78115c24","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6/GHSA-xqg2-r5rv-62x6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0069.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0170.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0170.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0169","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0169.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0068","title":"PHP PHP/FI mylog 脚本任意文件读取漏洞","description":"PHP/FI 的 mylog CGI 脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过构造特制的 URL 参数，读取目标服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 PHP/FI 1.0、FI 2.0 及 FI 2.0 b10 版本，利用方式简单，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0068"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:30.230","remediation":"立即移除服务器上 PHP/FI 1.0/2.0 的 mylog/mlog CGI 脚本文件，或升级至 PHP 3.0 及以上版本，该漏洞在后继版本中已修复。如无法升级，在 Web 服务器配置中禁止对该脚本的外部访问，并将 PHP/FI 替换为受支持的 PHP 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3396","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/713","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19553","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0068.json","https://github.com/Li